  "text": "Unrelated previous diagnoses included diabetes mellitus type 2, hyperlipidemia, and depression. The patient's family history was noncontributory with the exception of her daughter, who is currently being tested for POTS, which has a high concurrence rate with EDS-HT [CITATION_1] .",
